General.Name: Standard Premium Finance Holdings Inc.
General.Description: Standard Premium Finance Holdings, Inc. operates as an insurance premium financing company in the United States. It offers collateralized loans to businesses and individuals to finance the insurance premiums they pay on their commercial property and casualty insurance policies. The company was founded in 1991 and is based in Miami, Florida.
